Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.49,0:08:20.48,ED1-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\an9\fs40\shad0\bord1\blur3}生きとし生けるもの
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.76,0:08:23.79,ED1-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\an9\fs40\shad0\bord1\blur3}亡き者にはさせない！
